We can use get class method to return the runtime class definition of an object.

Synatx : public final Class getClass() throws 

Using this method we can access class level properties like methods and variables.

getClass() Method will be used in reflection activity to find the runtime implemenation of an interface. Ex: JDBC connectivity


=====================================================================
finalize() Method.

JVM's Garbage collector calls finalize method to perform cleanup activity before it takes the object to Garbage collection.
 Once finalize method compltes automaticlly GC destroyd that object
